metadata.name: ARIES
metadata.description:
This is Aries, a Fire sign, which governs impulses, initiative and action.
Aries feels a great need for independence, and her pioneering nature makes her feel better when she participates in exciting, challenging or new experiences.
Fearless enough to follow her own path, hates being told what to do.
